name: RoboOS
description: RoboOS The First Robotic Payment OS Powered by x402 stealth payments and ZK automation. Enable autonomous machine-to-machine payments, dynamic task allocation, and self-organizing robotic economies. RoboOS is the first-ever decentralized, privacy-preserving, programmable economic layer that allows robots to autonomously pay, bid, outsource, and settle tasks with one another. Powered by x402 stealth payment protocol and ZK automation, RoboOS enables autonomous machine economies.
